- Duke?
- David Duke.

00:47:27.089 --> 00:47:29.422
Atual Grande Mago
da Klan.

00:47:29.424 --> 00:47:31.224
Mas ele tá sempre
vestindo terno,

00:47:31.226 --> 00:47:34.160
